Patch Set 2:

(2 comments)

Here is the list of all the places in the code where uc_suppgids are set:

*** lustre/mdt/mdt_coordinator.c:
hsm_init_ucred[1036]           uc->uc_suppgids[0] = -1;
hsm_init_ucred[1037]           uc->uc_suppgids[1] = -1;

